{"tid":2311352,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 慢煮可樂唂咕牛面珠墩 配 香草牛油著蓉","createTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T02:15:48.000Z","uid":33359,"like":60,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc3191a9d211b74fe8a1b3ff6e185fff8cffad5","tid":2311352,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2D3GTXS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2D3GTXS.jpg&h=5c2a161d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFWYbKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFWYbKC.jpg&h=d83d3713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛面珠墩除咗有1，2舊仲未淋哂之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他都好淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入口即化咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能因為有落可樂同唂咕既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醬汁係有少少帶甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落好順喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著蓉唔算打得特別輕盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係配埋個牛肉汁一齊特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到成個身暖笠笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個肚仔好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講有個mewe觀塘飲食谷就黎2000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入谷入谷，永不為奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%B01&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=8dda801a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1</a>"},{"pid":"eab19b867a82b3b752f5a5295fb64829fcad3c54","tid":2311352,"uid":129695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb656ad056601d61484d4c383497a699cdcf1231","tid":2311352,"uid":211578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17325914f34fb57674ec7fd3cd8254a33fdedea1","tid":2311352,"uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"Where<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb013d5aea974b78e4edd98b45c2cdac83889e","tid":2311352,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"面豬師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb36c305eea8b6f450ff925ce41712feb826a6f","tid":2311352,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"早食師"},{"pid":"72cd0f8b7b3e43d0dda774c8c03c75b2f81f683a","tid":2311352,"uid":385480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb81e341351ee5e8f3c9be64b65831babeb33bf8","tid":2311352,"uid":114882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677b77b21876c5db537382f9c7c8cdb688c6785b","tid":2311352,"uid":114211,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maTzuRm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaTzuRm.gif&h=f0f4307b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai